race.comment: STROLL FUN (2) is a talented type and proved too strong last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 22.35 beating Super Cool. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Looks the testing material. SOUTHERN STAR (1) has a strong record this trip with six wins and four placings from 18 starts. Was out of placings last time (28.04) at this track in a Grade 4/5, finishing fifth and beaten 9 lengths. Looks a key chance on best figures. RUSTY ROCKET (8) continued his winning form with another strong run after leading to make it two on end at this track over 400m (22.76). Some good form is emerging from his last run. Hard to fault his form and he makes plenty of appeal. UNLEASHED MAYHEM (6) is worth some thought after placing in an impressive time last start.
